  "synopsis": "The adventures continue for Lula and her fellow Padawans in the Republic's golden age, an era set hundreds of years before the Skywalker Saga, when the Jedi were at their height and Master Yoda was much younger and still training Padawans in the field. Here Jedi Padawans Farzala and Qort take a break from the ongoing battle against the dangerous marauders known as the Nihil. As part of a secret mission, they join an aging Jedi Knight aboard the starship *The Vessel* to negotiate a peace treaty with the Hutt crime family. What could go wrong? As it turns out, literally everything.",
